QuestData.Title: Meet with Patrice Lancaster
QuestData.Description: I just received a scroll from the Training Hall, $n. Patrice Lancaster sends word that she wishes to speak with you. You should meet with her as soon as you can.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Patrice Lancaster at the Training Hall in Stormwind.
